>> Which one of the following statements is <strong>false?</strong>  <<

(x) Sentiment analysis is a <i>many-to-many</i>  sequence modelling task
( ) Named entity recognition is a <i>many-to-many</i> sequence modelling task {{ In named entity recognition, there is an output for every element of the input sequence}}
( ) Caption generation is a <i>one-to-many</i>  sequence modelling task {{ It is a <i>one-to-many</i> task since the output is a sentence for a single input}}  
( ) Machine translation is a <i>many-to-many</i>  sequence modelling task {{It is a <i>many-to-many</i>  task since the output is a sentence in another language }}
